l precision in the order of\njust a few milli-arcseconds. The result is a reliable set of high-quality\nassociations that are publicly available online.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Jun 2012 15:18:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 31 Oct 2012 13:23:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-05"}
