mensurate AF positions for underdoped and optimally doped materials\n(x<0.1), spin excitations in the over-doped side (x=0.15) form transversely\nincommensurate spin excitations, consistent with the RPA calculation.\nTherefore, the itinerant electron approach provides a reasonable description to\nthe low-energy AF spin excitations in BaFe2-xNixAs2.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Jun 2012 15:38:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 11 Jul 2012 09:03:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-07-12"}
